quran[18]{c,v,t}:
  9,122,"Haananaa gom…óim…ďe …ďen nde …ďe yahata (jihaadi) …ďe fow ma…ď…ďe. Ko ha…óno fedde kala e ma…ď…ďe yalta fii yo …ďe faamino ka diina, e fii yo …ďe jertin yim…ďe ma…ď…ďe …ďe si …ďe ruttitike e ma…ď…ďe, belajo'o, kam…ďe …ďe rentoto"
  9,123,"Ko onon yo gom…óim…ďe, ha…ďee …ďen …ďa…óii…ďe on immorde e heefer…ďe …ďen; yo …ďe taw e moo…óon √Īaande. Anndon pellet Alla no wonndi e gom…óu…ďe …ďen"
  9,124,"Si cortewol(simoore) jippinaama, hino e ma…ď…ďe on wi'oowo : \"ko hommbo e mo'on woni ko ngol …ďeydi gom…ói…ďal?\" Ammaa …ďen gom…óim…ďe, ngol …ďeydu …ďe gom…óinal, kam…ďe hi…ďe weltoo"
  9,125,"Ammma …ďen …ďen √Īawu woni ka …ďer…óe mun, ngol …ďeydu …ďe so…ďe e hoore so…ďe ma…ď…ďe, …ďe maayi ko …ďe heefer…ďe"
  9,126,"E …ďee yi'aali wonnde kam…ďe hi…ďe fitninee hitaande kala laawol maa laa…ďi …ói…ói? Refti …ďe tuubataa, …ďe wonnah waajitotoo…ďe"
  9,127,"Si tawii cortewol jippinaama, yoga ma…ď…ďe ndaara yoga […ďe wi'a] : \"Hara go…ó…óo no yi*a on?\" Refti …ďe ha…ďana. Alla surii …ďer…óe ma…ď…ďe tawde ko …ďe yim…ďe …ďe faamataa"
  9,128,"Gom…óii Nulaa…óo arii immorde e moo…óon, hino sa…óta e makko ko tampoton, rer…óu…óo e moo…óon, newanii…óo hinnotoo…óo(yurmotoodo) gom…óim…ďe …ďen"
  9,129,"Si …ďe huccitii(runtiima), maaku : \"Alla yonii lam. Alaa rewetee…óo si wanaa Kanko. Ko e Makko mi fawii; ko Kanko woni Jey…óo Arsi mawnu…óo on\". @Corrected"
  10,1,"Alif, laam, raa. ∆äen ko Aayeeje Deftere √Īe√Īaande nden"
  10,2,"Kere wonan yim…ďe …ďen kaawasee, fii Men wahyii- ma e gorko jeyaa…óo e ma…ď…ďe, wonnde : \"Jertin yim…ďe …ďen? Wewliniraa(weltina) gom…óim…ďe …ďen wonnde no woodani …ďe nokku goongaajo ka Joomi ma…ď…ďe? Heefer…ďe …ďen wi'i : \"Oo ko mbileejo fee√Īu…óo"
  10,3,"Pellet Joomi mon ko Alla on tagu…óo kammuuli …óin e leydi ndin nder bal…óe jeegoo, refti O fotondiri ka dow Arsi, himo toppitoo fiyakkuuji …óin. Alaa woo e tefoowo si wanaa …ďaawo duŇčayee Makko. Ko on mo'on woni Joomi moo…óon, rewee Mo. E on ciftortaho? @Corrected"
  10,4,"Ko ka Makko woni ruttorde mon on denndaangal, ko fodoore Alla goongunde! Ko kanko woni fu…ó…óude tagu ngun, refti O ruttita ngu fii yo O yo…ďa …ďen gom…óim…ďe …ďe golli golle mo∆ī∆īe e nun…óal. ∆Āen heefer…ďe kan, hino woodani …ďe njaram immorde e fatay…óam, e lepte muusu…óe sabu ko …ďe laatinoo hi…ďe yedda"
  10,5,"Ko kanko woni wa…óu…óo naange ngen jalbunge e lewru ndun nur…óundu, O e…ď…ďani ndu jippor…óe fii yo on anndu emmbere duu…ďi …óin e limoore nden. Alla tagiraali …óin si wanaa e goonga. Himo fensitana Aayeeje …óen yim…ďe anndoo…ďe"
  10,6,"Hino e luutindirgol jemma e √Īalorma ngol, e kon ko Alla tagi ka kammuuli e ka leydi, Maandeeji wonannde yim…ďe gom…óu…ďe"
  10,7,"∆Āen …ďe jortaaki hawrugol e Amen, …ďe weltori nguurndam aduna …óam, …ďe dee∆īiri …óam, e …ďen taw…ďe no welsindii e Aayeeje Amen …óen"
  10,8,"∆Āen, jaa∆īorde ma…ď…ďe nden ko Yiite ngen, sabu kon ko faggittonoo"
  10,9,"Pellet, …ďen gom…óim…ďe …ďe golli golle mo∆ī∆īe, Joomi ma…ď…ďe feewnay…ďe e gom…óinal ma…ď…ďe ngal. Can…ói no ila ley ma…ď…ďe ka Aljannaaji neema"
  10,10,"Noddaandu ma…ď…ďe nder ton, ko \"Ya Alla senaade woodaniima\", hiwrondiral ma…ď…ďe ngal ton, ko : \"Salaam\", [kisal]. Ko woni wattannde noddaandu ma…ď…ďe, ko : \"Yettoore woodanii Alla, Jey…óo Winndere nden"